       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CUSTOMER.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY CUSTMAST.
       01 WS-TOTAL-BALANCE    PIC 9(12)V99 VALUE 0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PROGRAM.
           DISPLAY "CUSTOMER PROCESSING".
           PERFORM PROCESS-CUSTOMER.
           DISPLAY "TOTAL: " WS-TOTAL-BALANCE.
           STOP RUN.

       PROCESS-CUSTOMER.
           IF CUST-ACTIVE
               ADD CUST-BALANCE TO WS-TOTAL-BALANCE
               DISPLAY "ACTIVE: " CUST-NAME
           ELSE
               DISPLAY "INACTIVE: " CUST-NAME
           END-IF.
